name: ENGLAND ON FIRE
description:
A psychic map of Albion. Inspired by the book of the same name.

Five endings. Made with Super Videotome.

Content Warnings
  • Psychological horror
  • Mass disappearance
  • Drowning
  • Medical dissection
  • Gore
  • Claustrophobia/binding
  • Colonialism/Christianisation
  • Transphobia
  • Death (Suffocation, crowd crush, burning, parasites/body invasion, overworking)
